SIMPLE: unpleaded
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unpleaded
<hw>Unpleaded</hw>  <def>See <er>pleaded</er>.</def>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unpleaded
<hw>Un*plead"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
used as a plea; not urged; <as>as, an <ex>unpleaded</ex>
excuse</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not supported by pleas; undefended; <as>as, an
<ex>unpleaded</ex> suit</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpleasant</ent>⟦br⟧
